WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:03.429
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:03.439 --> 00:00:05.030
I'm sorry I'm a little late. We went to

00:00:05.040 --> 00:00:08.549
church, and as I was sitting

00:00:08.559 --> 00:00:10.790
in church, the Lord gave me an open-eyed

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:12.790
vision about what we're supposed to be

00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:15.030
praying for tonight. So, we're just

00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:16.550
going to jump right into the river. But

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:19.189
I felt led to go over some of the

00:00:19.199 --> 00:00:22.150
things we saw yesterday when we were

00:00:22.160 --> 00:00:24.550
praying. Now, we had two videos

00:00:24.560 --> 00:00:28.470
yesterday. Some of you don't know it;

00:00:28.480 --> 00:00:30.950
the devil interfered with our internet,

00:00:30.960 --> 00:00:33.510
and so we just kept going and we ended

00:00:33.520 --> 00:00:35.430
up praying until almost

00:00:35.440 --> 00:00:36.950
morning,

00:00:36.960 --> 00:00:39.510
which was amazing. The glory of the

00:00:39.520 --> 00:00:42.709
Lord came in and hit me with

00:00:42.719 --> 00:00:44.790
Holy Ghost laughter. And I'm telling

00:00:44.800 --> 00:00:48.150
you, I've never done that to that

00:00:48.160 --> 00:00:51.750
level on a live stream. And so it

00:00:51.760 --> 00:00:54.950
was pretty amazing—the Lord was just

00:00:54.960 --> 00:00:57.910
bringing refreshing, especially to me

00:00:57.920 --> 00:01:00.310
and to my son and to my wife, and

00:01:00.320 --> 00:01:02.790
just blessing us. You know,

00:01:02.800 --> 00:01:05.030
when you are in a place of always

00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:06.950
pouring out, it's nice to get

00:01:06.960 --> 00:01:09.910
refreshed. And when you get a

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:12.230
touch from the Holy Spirit, it's

00:01:12.240 --> 00:01:13.990
refreshing. There's a lot of you

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:16.390
that don't know

00:01:16.400 --> 00:01:18.630
about it. And they say, 'Well, what is

00:01:18.640 --> 00:01:21.270
that? What were you doing?'That's just

00:01:21.280 --> 00:01:23.590
yielding. You can't make it

00:01:23.600 --> 00:01:25.749
happen, just like you can't make groaning

00:01:25.759 --> 00:01:27.510
happen. You get over in the flesh and

00:01:27.520 --> 00:01:31.190
you make things go and act weird, or you

00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:33.270
can laugh and be in the flesh, but I'd

00:01:33.280 --> 00:01:35.270
rather be in the flesh in church than

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:38.630
in the world, right? And so

00:01:38.640 --> 00:01:41.030
you start out—it's like people

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:42.630
say, 'How do you get over

00:01:42.630 --> 00:01:42.640
there?'You

00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:44.870
yield.

00:01:44.880 --> 00:01:47.030
You yield to the presence of God. You

00:01:47.040 --> 00:01:49.910
yield to the anointing. You yield. 'Holy

00:01:49.920 --> 00:01:52.630
Spirit, have your way. Have your way.

00:01:52.640 --> 00:01:55.109
You are the potter; I am the

00:01:55.119 --> 00:01:59.590
clay. I am yielded to you

00:01:59.590 --> 00:01:59.600
today.'When

00:01:59.600 --> 00:02:02.310
a pot is on the potter's wheel

00:02:02.320 --> 00:02:04.389
and it's molding, the pot doesn't say,

00:02:04.399 --> 00:02:05.590
'Well, I don't like the way you're

00:02:05.600 --> 00:02:07.030
pushing. I don't like the way you're

00:02:07.040 --> 00:02:09.990
doing. I want to be this

00:02:09.990 --> 00:02:10.000
way.'No,

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:12.949
it's yielded to the potter.

00:02:14.879 --> 00:02:17.270
Have your way. So, the potter's up there

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:19.510
pushing here, and he's putting all the

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:21.190
perfections out and doing all the things

00:02:21.200 --> 00:02:24.630
that he knows to do to make a good pot.

00:02:24.640 --> 00:02:27.190
And if you are a yielded vessel, the

00:02:27.200 --> 00:02:30.470
Holy Spirit will make a good pot.

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:32.309
Does that make sense? I'm trying to

00:02:32.319 --> 00:02:34.309
relate it. And so when you're going over

00:02:34.319 --> 00:02:35.910
into the laughter and you're

00:02:35.920 --> 00:02:38.229
just yielded, and it starts

00:02:38.239 --> 00:02:40.309
out with you just laughing and you feel that

00:02:40.319 --> 00:02:41.990
bubbling up inside

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:44.309
of you, the Holy Spirit will do

00:02:44.319 --> 00:02:46.070
it just like groanings. It's not

00:02:46.080 --> 00:02:48.869
something that you just fake. People go

00:02:48.879 --> 00:02:50.390
around acting weird and try to roll

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:52.949
around in the aisle and mock

00:02:52.959 --> 00:02:55.350
and try to imitate something, but when

00:02:55.360 --> 00:02:57.589
it's authentic and you feel the presence

00:02:57.599 --> 00:02:59.350
of God, it's like Braden said: 'Dad,

00:02:59.360 --> 00:03:01.350
the tangible presence of the Lord

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:03.750
was in our house last night. I could

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:06.309
feel it.'And you always

00:03:06.309 --> 00:03:06.319
wonder,

00:03:06.319 --> 00:03:08.869
because I don't want to

00:03:08.879 --> 00:03:11.430
be the only one having a good time.

00:03:11.440 --> 00:03:12.869
When you're at a party, you want

00:03:12.879 --> 00:03:14.229
everybody else to be having a good

00:03:14.239 --> 00:03:16.229
time, too, right? You're having a big

00:03:16.239 --> 00:03:18.070
party, you're celebrating, and Jesus is

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:20.149
there, and you're the only one

00:03:20.159 --> 00:03:21.990
acting crazy. I'd say

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:23.430
you're the only one in the

00:03:23.440 --> 00:03:24.869
town getting drunk. You're the town

00:03:24.879 --> 00:03:28.229
drunk.

00:03:28.239 --> 00:03:30.229
But whenever the Holy Ghost and fire is on

00:03:30.239 --> 00:03:32.149
you and everybody else is, it's like

00:03:32.159 --> 00:03:34.949
Acts chapter 2.

00:03:34.959 --> 00:03:37.110
It was just the third hour of the day,

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:38.869
right? It's just in the middle of

00:03:38.879 --> 00:03:41.990
the afternoon. 'Are these men

00:03:41.990 --> 00:03:42.000
drunk?'They're

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:45.270
all thinking

00:03:45.280 --> 00:03:48.229
they're all wasted, but they weren't.

00:03:48.239 --> 00:03:51.270
This is what this is. This is that

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:54.789
spoken by the prophet Joel:

00:03:54.799 --> 00:03:57.830
the day of Pentecost. And I truly

00:03:57.840 --> 00:04:00.390
believe that Jesus Christ is

00:04:00.400 --> 00:04:02.789
the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:04:02.799 --> 00:04:05.110
And he's still pouring out his spirit on

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:07.670
the church just like he did back in Acts

00:04:07.680 --> 00:04:11.030
chapter 2. I truly believe if you are a

00:04:11.040 --> 00:04:13.270
yielded vessel, we can walk in it. And

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:15.110
just like Pastor Candace, she

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:18.710
was teaching tonight about Moses.

00:04:18.720 --> 00:04:21.189
He was underneath the old covenant. How

00:04:21.199 --> 00:04:24.469
much more can we walk in the glory and

00:04:24.469 --> 00:04:24.479
be

00:04:24.479 --> 00:04:27.270
in the new covenant, the greater

00:04:27.280 --> 00:04:30.070
glory, and not just be somebody that

00:04:30.080 --> 00:04:31.830
is every once in a while

00:04:31.840 --> 00:04:34.550
visiting there, but somebody

00:04:34.560 --> 00:04:38.790
that lives there, lives in that presence,

00:04:38.800 --> 00:04:41.270
in that fullness of the glory, that

00:04:41.280 --> 00:04:43.749
people see it on you in these last days.

00:04:43.759 --> 00:04:45.749
So, all right. That's

00:04:45.759 --> 00:04:47.350
what all that was about. Last night was

00:04:47.360 --> 00:04:48.790
amazing. I loved it. And if you

00:04:48.800 --> 00:04:50.710
haven't watched that video, I encourage

00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:51.909
you, if you just want to have a

00:04:51.919 --> 00:04:54.950
refreshing, to go watch that video. As we

00:04:54.960 --> 00:04:57.749
were praying, the Lord showed me the

00:04:57.759 --> 00:05:01.030
revival again. And I saw Minneapolis,

00:05:01.040 --> 00:05:05.749
Minnesota, and I saw a well of revival

00:05:05.759 --> 00:05:09.029
springing forth out of the dirt. It

00:05:09.029 --> 00:05:09.039
started—do

00:05:09.039 --> 00:05:11.749
you know how you see

00:05:11.759 --> 00:05:14.790
cracks in the desert or in a big

00:05:14.800 --> 00:05:18.230
lake bed whenever the

00:05:18.240 --> 00:05:20.870
sun has dried up the water and the

00:05:20.870 --> 00:05:20.880
massive

00:05:20.880 --> 00:05:23.110
cracks are all in there? And you go,

00:05:23.120 --> 00:05:25.990
'Wow, this riverbed is really dry and you

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:29.029
can touch it.'But if

00:05:29.039 --> 00:05:32.710
you just dig down a little bit,

00:05:32.720 --> 00:05:35.350
the water is there. You

00:05:35.360 --> 00:05:39.029
just got to dig down a little bit. Well,

00:05:39.039 --> 00:05:42.070
the water table is always at a certain

00:05:42.080 --> 00:05:44.790
level. As I was

00:05:44.800 --> 00:05:48.150
praying into this, I saw the water

00:05:48.160 --> 00:05:50.790
coming from the fountains from the deep

00:05:50.800 --> 00:05:52.629
concerning the glory about what we're

00:05:52.639 --> 00:05:55.189
about to see. And the Lord said, 'Uncap

00:05:55.199 --> 00:05:59.029
the wells.'Uncap the wells. I saw the

00:05:59.039 --> 00:06:02.390
wells coming uncapped—what was, you

00:06:02.400 --> 00:06:04.390
know, when you cap a well and it was a

00:06:04.400 --> 00:06:07.029
springing forth of new water, new

00:06:07.039 --> 00:06:09.590
fountains of water. And all of a sudden,

00:06:09.600 --> 00:06:13.189
those cracks that were all in Minnesota

00:06:13.199 --> 00:06:15.909
started to fill up with water, and it was

00:06:15.919 --> 00:06:19.430
just barely touching the feet, just

00:06:19.440 --> 00:06:22.309
barely covering the soles of your shoes.

00:06:22.319 --> 00:06:25.110
And you're getting a little wet. But

00:06:25.120 --> 00:06:27.510
the Lord said, 'I'm going to take it up

00:06:27.520 --> 00:06:29.590
from where it's just on the

00:06:29.600 --> 00:06:33.029
soles of your shoes to ankle-deep, to

00:06:33.029 --> 00:06:33.039
knee-deep, to waist-deep,

00:06:33.039 --> 00:06:35.350
to over

00:06:35.360 --> 00:06:37.590
your head.'And he said, 'You can't mess

00:06:37.600 --> 00:06:39.909
this up.

00:06:39.919 --> 00:06:43.270
You're not big enough to mess this up

00:06:43.280 --> 00:06:46.309
for what I'm about to do—the harvest of

00:06:46.319 --> 00:06:48.629
the prayers

00:06:48.639 --> 00:06:51.590
for the intercessory prayer that has

00:06:51.590 --> 00:06:51.600
gone

00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:55.110
forth. The seeds of prayer are

00:06:55.120 --> 00:06:58.550
springing forth.'And the Lord said to us

00:06:58.560 --> 00:07:00.629
last night, 'Watch this.'And all of a

00:07:00.639 --> 00:07:02.950
sudden, bam, it was in Minnesota. Bam,

00:07:02.960 --> 00:07:05.430
it went to Tennessee. I saw around Perry

00:07:05.440 --> 00:07:08.230
Stone's area where he's at, his ministry,

00:07:08.230 --> 00:07:08.240
springing

00:07:08.240 --> 00:07:11.270
forth a well. And the Lord said,

00:07:11.280 --> 00:07:13.589
'Fill my cup,

00:07:13.589 --> 00:07:13.599
Lord.'I

00:07:13.599 --> 00:07:15.909
started singing that song, and the more I

00:07:15.919 --> 00:07:18.629
sang that song, the glory of the Lord

00:07:18.639 --> 00:07:22.070
started filling me. I could feel it.

00:07:22.080 --> 00:07:25.830
It went from Minnesota to Tennessee, to

00:07:25.840 --> 00:07:28.950
Mobile,

00:07:28.960 --> 00:07:31.510
Alabama, to Fort Worth, Texas,

00:07:31.520 --> 00:07:33.990
to Oklahoma City, to

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:37.110
Collinsville, to Tulsa, Oklahoma.

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:39.430
Boom, boom, boom. And it went to Nigeria,

00:07:39.440 --> 00:07:41.990
and it started springing forth wells of

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:44.230
revival. And the Lord said, 'I'm going

00:07:44.240 --> 00:07:47.830
to pour.'And I saw a wave of revival

00:07:47.840 --> 00:07:51.350
coming out of Minnesota again. I saw a

00:07:51.360 --> 00:07:54.629
wave of the glory of God coming forth

00:07:54.639 --> 00:07:56.629
out of it. And the Lord said, 'Pray for

00:07:56.639 --> 00:07:59.189
Mike Lindell. Pray for these people who

00:07:59.199 --> 00:08:02.230
are running for office in these areas,

00:08:02.240 --> 00:08:04.629
for Omar to find a new job

00:08:04.639 --> 00:08:06.790
somewhere else.

00:08:06.800 --> 00:08:09.270
Praying for revival.

00:08:09.280 --> 00:08:12.550
Praying for this major

00:08:12.550 --> 00:08:12.560
harvest.'And

00:08:12.560 --> 00:08:15.510
I could see it going, and it

00:08:15.520 --> 00:08:17.990
was touching down in these cities. And he

00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:20.309
said, 'These are

00:08:20.309 --> 00:08:20.319
places

00:08:23.589 --> 00:08:23.599
of

00:08:23.599 --> 00:08:25.670
harbingers,

00:08:25.680 --> 00:08:29.029
like

00:08:29.039 --> 00:08:32.070
harvesters, like

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:34.630
crop circles. I don't know how else to

00:08:34.640 --> 00:08:38.870
say it. There are glory

00:08:38.870 --> 00:08:38.880
zones—better

00:08:38.880 --> 00:08:41.589
glory zones, glory manifested

00:08:41.599 --> 00:08:44.550
zones, designated

00:08:44.560 --> 00:08:48.470
chosen places for the revival that God

00:08:48.480 --> 00:08:50.790
has put his finger on.'And when I told

00:08:50.800 --> 00:08:54.310
you I saw the hand of the Lord—five

00:08:54.310 --> 00:08:54.320
of it—all

00:08:54.320 --> 00:08:57.430
his fingers went out

00:08:57.440 --> 00:09:01.030
over the earth and shafts of light

00:09:01.040 --> 00:09:04.150
shot down from his fingers and made

00:09:04.160 --> 00:09:06.949
pillars of light coming from his

00:09:06.959 --> 00:09:09.509
fingers. And he said, 'These are the

00:09:09.519 --> 00:09:13.990
places that I have designated for a

00:09:14.000 --> 00:09:17.030
major harvest of souls in the last days

00:09:17.040 --> 00:09:19.269
in Tennessee, in these

00:09:19.269 --> 00:09:19.279
areas.'And

00:09:19.279 --> 00:09:21.990
there were shafts of light that

00:09:22.000 --> 00:09:25.110
shot forth, and there was major revival

00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:28.230
in America and parts of Australia

00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:30.790
and Asia and the Middle East,

00:09:30.800 --> 00:09:33.509
Europe, and Africa. And I'm telling you,

00:09:33.519 --> 00:09:36.230
ladies and gentlemen, as

00:09:36.240 --> 00:09:40.230
these shafts of glory came out of the

00:09:40.240 --> 00:09:42.870
Lord's hand, he said, "I designated

00:09:42.880 --> 00:09:46.710
these places. I saw satanic camps trying

00:09:46.720 --> 00:09:49.670
to camp themselves around and about these

00:09:49.680 --> 00:09:53.110
areas to try to prevent the glory from

00:09:53.120 --> 00:09:55.430
coming. But they're no match for our

00:09:55.440 --> 00:09:58.230
heavenly Father. No

00:09:58.240 --> 00:10:00.870
matter how big the devil tries to

00:10:00.880 --> 00:10:04.949
be, even on his best day, he's nothing.

00:10:04.959 --> 00:10:07.910
He's a loser. He's been defeated.

00:10:07.920 --> 00:10:09.430
And that's what I was trying to tell you

00:10:09.440 --> 00:10:13.110
all. Do you believe that God

00:10:13.120 --> 00:10:16.069
can make mistakes? Do you believe that

00:10:16.079 --> 00:10:18.790
you're a mistake? That God made

00:10:18.800 --> 00:10:20.790
a mistake by letting you be here for

00:10:20.800 --> 00:10:22.630
such a time as this? And that was my

00:10:22.640 --> 00:10:24.389
point in coming across last night when

00:10:24.399 --> 00:10:27.590
the Lord told me to ask them that.

00:10:27.600 --> 00:10:30.069
I don't believe that our heavenly Father

00:10:30.079 --> 00:10:32.710
can ever make a mistake.

00:10:32.720 --> 00:10:36.550
We are fearfully

00:10:36.560 --> 00:10:39.430
and wonderfully made, every single one of

00:10:39.440 --> 00:10:41.350
us. And we have been called to the

00:10:41.360 --> 00:10:44.069
kingdom for such a time as this. And

00:10:44.079 --> 00:10:46.630
it's time for you, behind this

00:10:46.640 --> 00:10:48.630
camera right now, to get a backbone like

00:10:48.640 --> 00:10:52.310
a crowbar and expect the

00:10:52.310 --> 00:10:52.320
unexpected—to

00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:55.269
be expecting God to do something huge

00:10:55.279 --> 00:10:57.910
through you.

00:10:57.920 --> 00:11:00.389
It just takes one

00:11:00.399 --> 00:11:03.110
spark

00:11:03.120 --> 00:11:05.509
to light a whole forest fire. And he

00:11:05.519 --> 00:11:07.670
said, 'Pray for the revival.'And then

00:11:07.680 --> 00:11:09.430
he said, 'Pray for

00:11:09.440 --> 00:11:11.509
Elon

00:11:11.509 --> 00:11:11.519
Musk.'There's

00:11:11.519 --> 00:11:14.150
enough here even right now that

00:11:14.160 --> 00:11:15.990
we can pray that Elon Musk would have a

00:11:16.000 --> 00:11:19.110
visitation. I saw to pray for Elon Musk

00:11:19.120 --> 00:11:21.509
again. He said, 'I'm calling him in. I'm

00:11:21.519 --> 00:11:24.470
calling him.'Well, 'He's too dark. I

00:11:24.480 --> 00:11:27.350
don't know. He'll never.'No. The Lord

00:11:27.360 --> 00:11:29.910
said as I was being persecuted on

00:11:29.920 --> 00:11:31.829
Facebook, they

00:11:33.440 --> 00:11:35.030
told me they'd call me, and then they

00:11:35.040 --> 00:11:36.630
told me they'd call me again, and they

00:11:36.640 --> 00:11:38.550
keep giving me the runaround. And

00:11:38.560 --> 00:11:40.630
that's when I said, 'Lord, why is it the body of

00:11:40.640 --> 00:11:45.030
Christ doesn't have a faith book? Why

00:11:45.040 --> 00:11:47.269
is it that the body of Christ

00:11:47.269 --> 00:11:47.279
is

00:11:47.279 --> 00:11:49.430
always having to

00:11:49.440 --> 00:11:52.710
use what's the trend? Why are we not

00:11:52.720 --> 00:11:54.790
the

00:11:54.790 --> 00:11:54.800
trendsetters?

00:11:54.800 --> 00:11:56.870
Why is Facebook the leader? Why is

00:11:56.880 --> 00:11:59.509
Instagram the leader? Why is TikTok

00:11:59.509 --> 00:11:59.519
the

00:11:59.519 --> 00:12:01.509
leader? Why is the body of

00:12:01.519 --> 00:12:04.630
Christ not the head?'And he talked about

00:12:04.640 --> 00:12:07.509
the money, because the body

00:12:07.519 --> 00:12:09.030
of Christ chokes on money. You go, 'Well,

00:12:09.040 --> 00:12:10.629
we can't have that. You know,

00:12:10.639 --> 00:12:12.069
the love of money is the root of all

00:12:12.069 --> 00:12:12.079
evil.'But

00:12:12.079 --> 00:12:13.670
that's why I said

00:12:13.680 --> 00:12:15.509
you're ignorant: because the Lord wants

00:12:15.519 --> 00:12:17.829
