00:43:19.109 --> 00:43:19.119
wildernesses

00:43:19.119 --> 00:43:20.950
because they're too dangerous

00:43:20.960 --> 00:43:23.750
for the applause of man. I lived hidden.

00:43:23.760 --> 00:43:26.069
I died hidden. And yet my prayers still

00:43:26.079 --> 00:43:29.030
echo eternity. Hidden intercession is

00:43:29.040 --> 00:43:32.069
not a punishment. It's a promotion. When

00:43:32.079 --> 00:43:34.230
God hides you, he's trusting you to

00:43:34.240 --> 00:43:37.270
