00:43:37.280 --> 00:43:39.670
towns I would never see again. I laid

00:43:39.680 --> 00:43:42.230
foundations for revivals that would come

00:43:42.240 --> 00:43:45.109
after I died. That's the mark of true

00:43:45.119 --> 00:43:47.270
intercession. It builds altars for the

00:43:47.280 --> 00:43:49.670
next generation to burn upon. You may

00:43:49.680 --> 00:43:51.829
never see the fruit, but the fire will

00:43:51.839 --> 00:43:55.109
fall. Stop asking, "What did I

00:43:55.109 --> 00:43:55.119
build?"Start

00:43:55.119 --> 00:43:57.589
asking, "Did I

00:43:57.589 --> 00:43:57.599
obey?"Faithfulness

00:43:57.599 --> 00:44:00.069
is measured in eternity,

00:44:00.079 --> 00:44:02.550
not Instagram likes.

00:44:02.560 --> 00:44:04.390
When Finney stood before thousands, I

00:44:04.400 --> 00:44:06.470
stood before God. When he gave the altar

00:44:06.480 --> 00:44:08.790
call, I stood at the heavenly gates

00:44:08.800 --> 00:44:11.510
pleading for mercy. When he rested, I

00:44:11.520 --> 00:44:13.910
wrestled. You may feel unseen, but you

00:44:13.920 --> 00:44:16.069
are known in the courts of heaven. And

00:44:16.079 --> 00:44:18.150
when you step into eternity, you'll

00:44:18.160 --> 00:44:19.990
discover that your hidden life was a

00:44:20.000 --> 00:44:25.990
highway for revival.

00:44:26.000 --> 00:44:27.750
There's a sound that doesn't come from

00:44:27.760 --> 00:44:30.069
the mouth. It comes from the spirit.

00:44:30.079 --> 00:44:33.270
It's the sound of travail. It's the cry

00:44:33.280 --> 00:44:35.589
of a soul in sync with the heartbeat of

00:44:35.599 --> 00:44:38.390
God. And I'll tell you this, that sound

00:44:38.400 --> 00:44:41.030
shakes principalities. I've heard demons

00:44:41.040 --> 00:44:42.870
scream in the spirit realm when a true

00:44:42.880 --> 00:44:44.790
intercessor groaned under the weight of

00:44:44.800 --> 00:44:47.430
divine burden. You don't have to yell to

00:44:47.440 --> 00:44:49.750
terrorize darkness. Hell doesn't fear

00:44:49.760 --> 00:44:52.150
volume. It fears authority. And

00:44:52.160 --> 00:44:55.270
authority comes from intimacy. When you

00:44:55.280 --> 00:44:57.510
pray with heaven's permission and the

00:44:57.520 --> 00:44:59.750
