00:45:05.200 --> 00:45:07.030
I didn't come to intercession with

00:45:07.040 --> 00:45:09.750
formulas. I came with desperation. And

00:45:09.760 --> 00:45:12.470
when your desperation becomes holy, it

00:45:12.480 --> 00:45:15.109
turns into something beautiful. A sound

00:45:15.119 --> 00:45:17.910
that bends the heavens. It's the sound

00:45:17.920 --> 00:45:20.790
of Jesus in Gethsemane.

00:45:20.800 --> 00:45:23.030
The sound of Hannah in the temple. The

00:45:23.040 --> 00:45:25.349
sound of the spirit groaning through

00:45:25.359 --> 00:45:28.309
yielded vessels. That sound terrifies

00:45:28.319 --> 00:45:31.430
every power of darkness. When you truly

00:45:31.440 --> 00:45:33.750
walk in prevailing intercession, you

00:45:33.760 --> 00:45:36.550
become a mobile altar. Demons sense

00:45:36.560 --> 00:45:39.030
you before you say a word.

00:45:39.030 --> 00:45:39.040
Environments

00:45:39.040 --> 00:45:41.270
shift when you enter rooms. Your spirit

00:45:41.280 --> 00:45:43.510
carries residue from the secret place.

00:45:43.520 --> 00:45:46.069
And everything unclean takes notice.

00:45:46.079 --> 00:45:48.630
This isn't religion. This is war. And

00:45:48.640 --> 00:45:54.470
your groan is your battle

00:45:54.470 --> 00:45:54.480
cry.

00:45:54.480 --> 00:45:56.630
I reached places in intercession where I

00:45:56.640 --> 00:45:58.550
was no longer praying. I was

00:45:58.560 --> 00:46:01.190
being prayed through. My mind was still,

00:46:01.200 --> 00:46:03.750
but the groans came like waves. The

00:46:03.760 --> 00:46:06.390
spirit took over. I became a vessel. My

00:46:06.400 --> 00:46:09.349
words left. My will surrendered. And in

00:46:09.359 --> 00:46:11.270
those holy moments, I felt like I

00:46:11.280 --> 00:46:13.349
touched the edge of eternity. That's

00:46:13.359 --> 00:46:15.750
where real intercession begins. You

00:46:15.760 --> 00:46:18.390
don't push your agenda. You host his.

00:46:18.400 --> 00:46:20.550
You don't ask for things. You become a

00:46:20.560 --> 00:46:24.150
conduit for his divine will.

00:46:24.160 --> 00:46:26.470
The spirit searches the mind of God and

00:46:26.480 --> 00:46:28.710
pours it through you like fire down a

00:46:28.720 --> 00:46:31.910
pipe. I remember times I'd be walking

00:46:31.920 --> 00:46:34.550
and suddenly feel a crushing weight fall

00:46:34.560 --> 00:46:36.950
on my soul. I'd collapse in prayer,

00:46:36.960 --> 00:46:39.349
often in unexpected places. The Lord

00:46:39.359 --> 00:46:41.430
would drop a burden on me so heavy I

00:46:41.440 --> 00:46:44.069
couldn't move until it lifted. That's

00:46:44.079 --> 00:46:45.910
not emotionalism. That's spiritual

00:46:45.910 --> 00:46:45.920
possession—not

00:46:45.920 --> 00:46:48.069
by a demon, but by the

00:46:48.079 --> 00:46:50.710
Holy Ghost. God is looking for people he

00:46:50.720 --> 00:46:52.710
can trust with his burden. Not people

00:46:52.720 --> 00:46:54.550
who will treat it like a goosebump, but

00:46:54.560 --> 00:46:56.790
like a baby in the womb—something that

00:46:56.800 --> 00:46:58.950
must be carried until it's birthed in

00:46:58.960 --> 00:47:00.150
the

00:47:00.150 --> 00:47:00.160
earth.'I

00:47:00.160 --> 00:47:02.870
love that.

00:47:02.880 --> 00:47:04.790
It's carrying it in prayer

00:47:05.599 --> 00:47:08.390
until it's birthed in the earth.

