00:47:20.720 --> 00:47:24.069
Through intercession. Keep going.

00:47:24.079 --> 00:47:27.190
'I didn't need to prepare fancy words. I

00:47:27.200 --> 00:47:29.270
didn't need eloquence. I just needed

00:47:29.280 --> 00:47:31.589
