00:47:42.640 --> 00:47:50.069
of intercession breaks regions.

00:47:50.079 --> 00:47:52.309
The prophet Joel described it best: Let

00:47:52.319 --> 00:47:54.150
the priest weep between the porch and

00:47:54.160 --> 00:47:56.390
the altar. That image never left me.

00:47:56.400 --> 00:47:58.230
That place between the entryway and the

00:47:58.240 --> 00:48:00.950
