00:48:10.640 --> 00:48:13.270
the church to awaken. God honors the

00:48:13.280 --> 00:48:15.109
tears of intercessors more than the

00:48:15.119 --> 00:48:17.750
applause of preachers. There are natural

00:48:17.760 --> 00:48:19.910
tears and then there are spirit-born

00:48:19.910 --> 00:48:19.920
tears.'I

00:48:19.920 --> 00:48:22.150
didn't cry because I was

00:48:22.160 --> 00:48:24.150
emotional. I cried because the burden

00:48:24.160 --> 00:48:26.870
was so heavy it crushed my heart open.

00:48:26.880 --> 00:48:29.349
Those tears were prophetic. They

00:48:29.359 --> 00:48:31.510
carried the weight of regions. They were

00:48:31.520 --> 00:48:33.270
mixed with heaven's grief and heaven's

00:48:33.280 --> 00:48:35.750
hope. Sometimes a single tear from an

00:48:35.760 --> 00:48:37.589
