00:48:42.319 --> 00:48:43.910
You've come close enough to the presence

00:48:43.920 --> 00:48:45.990
to be transformed, but you're still

00:48:46.000 --> 00:48:47.910
standing in the gap for others. You

00:48:47.920 --> 00:48:49.990
haven't stepped into glory for yourself.

00:48:50.000 --> 00:48:51.510
You're pulling others in with your

00:48:51.520 --> 00:48:54.549
tears. That place is painful, but it's

00:48:54.559 --> 00:48:57.349
also holy. And that is where revival is

00:48:57.359 --> 00:49:01.589
born.

